name: Dream of Space
description: Astronauts are people who always love the top of the clouds and want to always flying. But this astronaut in our story, what he has seen from astronauts is just astronaut clothes, and with his imagination and the calm he has taken from the sea, he has caused him to go to the clouds and do his sports activities, but it is only a dream. Is that he is surrounded all around and can’t get out of it
